            { title: 'Instant Journal Formatting', description: 'Authors write their raw manuscript in the platform; when ready to publish, they select "Nature" from a dropdown menu, and the platform autonomously restructures the entire Word document (margins, fonts, citation style) to perfectly match Nature’s strict submission guidelines.' },
            { title: 'Literature Matrix Generation', description: 'Students select 10 different PDFs; the AI physically reads all 10 simultaneously and constructs a custom spreadsheet comparing their methodologies, limitations, and sample sizes, entirely automating days of manual data-entry.' }
