            { title: 'Automated CRM Updates', description: 'Sales Account Executives finish a complex discovery call, and Sembly automatically extracts the client’s budget, timeline, and requested features, seamlessly pushing those customized data fields directly into Salesforce or HubSpot without manual data entry.' },
            { title: 'Bilingual Meeting Support', description: 'Global remote teams conduct meetings where members speak in overlapping languages; Sembly automatically transcribes and translates the conversations, ensuring the final English executive summary accurately reflects the intent of the French speaker.' }
